docs.abstract: With online banks offering certificates of deposit that pay more than 2 percent, some experts suggest putting cash in several C.D.s with different terms.

docs.abstract: The Facebook chief executive said the next wave of social networking would be to enable private and encrypted discussions.
docs.snippet: The Facebook chief executive said the next wave of social networking would be to enable private and encrypted discussions.
docs.lead_paragraph: SAN FRANCISCO — Social networking has long been predicated on people sharing their status updates, photos and messages with the world. Now Mark Zuckerberg, chief executive of Facebook, plans to start shifting people toward private conversations and away from public broadcasting.

headline.main: Facebook’s Mark Zuckerberg Says He’ll Shift Focus to Users’ Privacy
headline.print_headline: Users’ Privacy Is New Focus, Facebook Says

docs.abstract: No one knows when the special counsel will file his report on Russian interference in the 2016 election, or whether the public will see it. But two publishers aren’t waiting.
docs.snippet: No one knows when the special counsel will file his report on Russian interference in the 2016 election, or whether the public will see it. But two publishers aren’t waiting.
docs.lead_paragraph: The legions of reporters and commentators following every move by Robert S. Mueller III, the special counsel, do not know when he will finish investigating Russian interference in the 2016 election. And it is unclear whether the report he is expected to file will ever become public.
